    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Thanks for the demo, it really clarifies the issue. Worth nothing `:focus-visible` support is lacking:\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/2982512/135858871-7883f2db-57e2-4d88-9674-c110ff0263f5.png)\r\nsource: https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/:focus-visible#browser_compatibility\r\n\r\nI guess as we try to refine the \"what good looks like\" aspect of things, this could totally make sense!",
